      "id": 6350,
      "name": "Paul",
      "username": "Trax101",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/trax101/{size}/938_2.png",
      "created_at": "2022-04-05T19:34:35.945Z",
      "cooked": "<p>The workout database is so vast a random workout button would be great. It could be implemented so the user sets a max time or workout type (VO2, threshold, etc) or both.</p>\n<p>Personally I\u2019m thinking a dumb version of the TrainerRoad adaptive workout or Garmin suggested workout. Although maybe it would become a pre-curser to a TrainerDay equivalent.</p>",
