    {
      "id": 6736,
      "name": "Paul",
      "username": "Trax101",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/trax101/{size}/938_2.png",
      "created_at": "2022-06-11T14:41:20.714Z",
      "cooked": "<p>With only one vote and no comments I\u2019m not sure I conveyed my idea very well (or maybe no one else was interested in it). But, I will try one more time.</p>\n<p>I don\u2019t feel trainerday makes it very easy for me to find new and different workouts. When using the trainerday search no randomisation is applied to the results, by default they are displayed by popularity which only keeps the same workouts in the first few pages. The below images show when using a search term across the apps at various times the results are always displayed the same.</p>\n<p>PC Search<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/f/fd045860932af17d37524af27c610c355f2d3412.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/fd045860932af17d37524af27c610c355f2d3412\" title=\"PC-Search\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/fd045860932af17d37524af27c610c355f2d3412_2_623x500.jpeg\" alt=\"PC-Search\" data-base62-sha1=\"A6i6No3vZV4yGr9sYst8xwJGfp8\" width=\"623\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/fd045860932af17d37524af27c610c355f2d3412_2_623x500.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/fd045860932af17d37524af27c610c355f2d3412_2_934x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/f/fd045860932af17d37524af27c610c355f2d3412.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/fd045860932af17d37524af27c610c355f2d3412_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">PC-Search</span><span class=\"informations\">1233\u00d7988 232 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>iPad Search<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/a/abd922714f7778a1c576c2d8cfb355fd0c63a735.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/abd922714f7778a1c576c2d8cfb355fd0c63a735\" title=\"iPad-Search\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/abd922714f7778a1c576c2d8cfb355fd0c63a735_2_690x479.jpeg\" alt=\"iPad-Search\" data-base62-sha1=\"oweR4GcQikN3vgNoMreZrRN4HRz\" width=\"690\" height=\"479\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/abd922714f7778a1c576c2d8cfb355fd0c63a735_2_690x479.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/abd922714f7778a1c576c2d8cfb355fd0c63a735_2_1035x718.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/a/abd922714f7778a1c576c2d8cfb355fd0c63a735.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/abd922714f7778a1c576c2d8cfb355fd0c63a735_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">iPad-Search</span><span class=\"informations\">1180\u00d7820 99.4 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>iPhone Search<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/1/100a456e9fa3464a2f532f09daf2ea3251956790.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/100a456e9fa3464a2f532f09daf2ea3251956790\" title=\"iPhone-Search\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/100a456e9fa3464a2f532f09daf2ea3251956790_2_231x500.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone-Search\" data-base62-sha1=\"2hTE1lNu3oHyL9bfPmf5BlG1jmU\" width=\"231\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/100a456e9fa3464a2f532f09daf2ea3251956790_2_231x500.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/100a456e9fa3464a2f532f09daf2ea3251956790_2_346x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/100a456e9fa3464a2f532f09daf2ea3251956790_2_462x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/100a456e9fa3464a2f532f09daf2ea3251956790_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">iPhone-Search</span><span class=\"informations\">585\u00d71266 125 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Google uses a \u2018I\u2019m Feeling Lucky\u2019 button on its search page. What I was trying to suggest was, something like this could be added next to the search button on the mobile apps.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/3/3da83bbd818fcb3b94fbff0889fceac134074ea1.jpeg\" alt=\"Google\" data-base62-sha1=\"8NryY3iGZxEqtIaBHnd8Am2N3bj\" width=\"688\" height=\"351\"></p>\n<p>It would mean, we could enter a search term such as: \u2018Zone: Anaerobic 60 mins\u2019 press a random / I\u2019m Feeling Lucky button to open a random workout from the vast databases which I am sure most people only look at a fraction off.</p>",
